Package: centrimpact
Type: Package
Title: Supporting the Analysis and Visualization of Community Engaged Research Metrics
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jeremy", "Price",
      email = "jfprice@iu.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6506-3526")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for analyzing and visualizing community-engaged research 
    metrics within the CEnTR-IMPACT framework. The package includes functions for 
    network analysis, diversity calculations, proportional scaling, and creating 
    consistent visualizations with customizable color palettes and typography. 
    Designed to support researchers in evaluating community engagement outcomes 
    and impact across multiple domains and network layers.
